        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "id": "gallery_character15233",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/b169256454759e4824bdb7fc169850fc_3229114703586276700.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Pari are very mysterious creatures. And as the \"Bloomguard\" of her race, Sorush can replace your characters to fly and move.</p><p>When Sorush is in flight, your character will stay in place to await her return.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/4"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character55224",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/55f6f903b9c70c91fd37f26798fc891f_4054217950471186362.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>While in flight, Sorush can ascend or descend, and can use the Accelerate skill to increase her flight speed.</p><p>Sorush cannot be too far from your character, though. A Bloomguard should never abandon others, after all.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/4"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character85023",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/1b12c7048c39a009cc5b433f67b6a4db_9012985615599091374.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Sorush can call upon the special energies within items around which <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">mysterious mayflies dance</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Press Sorush's Interact skill</span> to allow her to use her power to guide the might of Khvarena.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Hold her Interact skill</span> to cause her to stop and continuously channel Khvarena's might. During this time, you can control your character freely.</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/4"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character97407",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/8b1b527dfd3fd9eb3c09eeefdd24531d_3053592629829659364.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>As a Pari, Sorush can also perceive some things beyond normal human sight...</p>",
                "key": "Page 4/4"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
